The "Course in Applied Artificial Intelligence" offered by 4Geeks Academy is a 6-week program designed for professionals interested in leveraging AI within their current roles. The course covers various types of generative AI, as well as key elements like context, prompts, and models. By the end of the course, participants will be equipped with the tools and best practices needed to optimize AI integration and enhance workplace capabilities. The course includes 2 live, online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 12 people. No previous experience is required, and participants will receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. For more information, visit the website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop